{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1391580/extras/FPS_RPG_Finishers_1.gif?t=1737140180\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Modular Singleplayer Campaign</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ESCAPE CONDITION combines fast-paced FPS combat with a rich story and environment determined by your choices. Each mission asks you to make a difficult decision regarding the path of an AI branch that The Future Resistance has warned you will have catastrophic consequences for their time. Will you choose to do the bidding of The Resistance by preventing the AI branch from being released? Or will you take advantage of the AI Branch by installing a powerful Cybernetic created by it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The choice is yours. When you've made your choices, fight for the world you've created, battling against the Midtown government and Baydentic, the megacorporation controlling the direction of society with their advanced AI technologies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Intense first-person shooter combat merged with world building not seen in many FPS games. Every choice you make alters your character, the map, and/or NPCs in some way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The first three missions serve as world building missions, choose carefully to determine the map's Chaos, Pollution, and Technology levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Singleplayer campaign features light RPG leveling in addition to world building impacts of your choices.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perform finishers to partially refill your Focus meter and health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle against the takeover of AI with help from The Future Resistance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Digitally painted UI art, hand-crafted maps with sharp attention to detail</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_p